No, there is a powdercoat zinc primer for marine purposes that he should 
apply before the black 80% gloss powdercoat layer.

> Now about the  color, what is 80% gloss semi-gloss black powdercoat ???  i
> just ask him about putting this ??  maybe i could buy the powder somewhere 
> and bring it to him, my first thought was to use a satin black !!

Well 80% gloss is a semi-gloss that matches the original VW factory 
semi-gloss black of the engine tin.

